  "root_text": {
    "sn22.52:0.1": "Saṁyutta Nikāya 22.52 ",
    "sn22.52:0.2": "5. Attadīpavagga ",
    "sn22.52:0.3": "Dutiyanandikkhayasutta ",
    "sn22.52:1.1": "Sāvatthinidānaṁ. ",
    "sn22.52:1.2": "“Rūpaṁ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasi karotha, rūpāniccatañca yathābhūtaṁ samanupassatha. ",
    "sn22.52:1.3": "Rūpaṁ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yoniso manasi karonto, rūpāniccatañca yathābhūtaṁ samanupassanto rūpasmiṁ nibbindati. ",
    "sn22.52:1.4": "Nandikkhayā rāgakkhayo, rāgakkhayā nandikkhayo. ",
    "sn22.52:1.5": "Nandirāgakkhayā cittaṁ vimuttaṁ suvimuttanti vuccati. ",
    "sn22.52:1.6": "Vedanaṁ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasi karotha, vedanāniccatañca yathābhūtaṁ samanupassatha. ",
    "sn22.52:1.7": "Vedanaṁ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yoniso manasi karonto, vedanāniccatañca yathābhūtaṁ samanupassanto vedanāya nibbindati. ",
    "sn22.52:1.8": "Nandikkhayā rāgakkhayo, rāgakkhayā nandikkhayo. ",
    "sn22.52:1.9": "Nandirāgakkhayā cittaṁ vimuttaṁ suvimuttanti vuccati. ",
    "sn22.52:1.10": "Saññaṁ bhikkhave … ",
    "sn22.52:1.11": "saṅkhāre, bhikkhave, yoniso manasi karotha, saṅkhārāniccatañca yathābhūtaṁ samanupassatha. ",
    "sn22.52:1.12": "Saṅkhāre, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yoniso manasi karonto, saṅkhārāniccataṁ yathābhūtaṁ samanupassanto saṅkhāresu nibbindati. ",
    "sn22.52:1.13": "Nandikkhayā rāgakkhayo, rāgakkhayā nandikkhayo. ",
    "sn22.52:1.14": "Nandirāgakkhayā cittaṁ vimuttaṁ suvimuttanti vuccati. ",
    "sn22.52:1.15": "Viññāṇaṁ, bhikkhave, yoniso manasi karotha, viññāṇāniccatañca yathābhūtaṁ samanupassatha. ",
    "sn22.52:1.16": "Viññāṇaṁ, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yoniso manasi karonto, viññāṇāniccatañca yathābhūtaṁ samanupassanto viññāṇasmiṁ nibbindati. ",
    "sn22.52:1.17": "Nandikkhayā rāgakkhayo, rāgakkhayā nandikkhayo. ",
    "sn22.52:1.18": "Nandirāgakkhayā cittaṁ vimuttaṁ suvimuttanti vuccatī”ti. ",
    "sn22.52:1.19": "Dasamaṁ. ",
    "sn22.52:1.20": "Attadīpavaggo pañcamo. ",
    "sn22.52:2.0": "Tassuddānaṁ ",
    "sn22.52:2.1": "Attadīpā paṭipadā, ",
    "sn22.52:2.2": "Dve ca honti aniccatā; ",
    "sn22.52:2.3": "Samanupassanā khandhā, ",
    "sn22.52:2.4": "Dve soṇā dve nandikkhayena cāti. ",
    "sn22.52:2.5": "Mūlapaṇṇāsako samatto. ",
    "sn22.52:3.0": "Tassa mūlapaṇṇāsakassa vagguddānaṁ ",
    "sn22.52:3.1": "Nakulapitā anicco ca, ",
    "sn22.52:3.2": "Bhāro natumhākena ca; ",
    "sn22.52:3.3": "Attadīpena paññāso, ",
    "sn22.52:3.4": "Paṭhamo tena pavuccatīti. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "sn22.52:0.1": "Linked Discourses 22.52 ",
    "sn22.52:0.2": "5. Be Your Own Island ",
    "sn22.52:0.3": "The End of Relishing (2nd) ",
    "sn22.52:1.1": "At Sāvatthī. ",
    "sn22.52:1.2": "“Mendicants, rationally apply the mind to form. Truly see the impermanence of form. ",
    "sn22.52:1.3": "When a mendicant does this, they grow disillusioned with form. ",
    "sn22.52:1.4": "When relishing ends, greed ends. When greed ends, relishing ends. ",
    "sn22.52:1.5": "When relishing and greed end, the mind is freed, and is said to be well freed. ",
    "sn22.52:1.6": "Rationally apply the mind to feeling … ",
    "sn22.52:1.7": "",
    "sn22.52:1.8": "",
    "sn22.52:1.9": "",
    "sn22.52:1.10": "perception … ",
    "sn22.52:1.11": "choices … ",
    "sn22.52:1.12": "",
    "sn22.52:1.13": "",
    "sn22.52:1.14": "",
    "sn22.52:1.15": "consciousness. Truly see the impermanence of consciousness. ",
    "sn22.52:1.16": "When a mendicant does this, they grow disillusioned with consciousness. ",
    "sn22.52:1.17": "When relishing ends, greed ends. When greed ends, relishing ends. ",
    "sn22.52:1.18": "When relishing and greed end, the mind is freed, and is said to be well freed.” ",
    "sn22.52:1.19": "",
